[[module CSS]]
.art-container {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    align-content: center;
    justify-content: space-around;
    align-self: flex-end
    gap: 1rem 1rem;
}
.art-container .art {
    flex: 0 3 150px;
    text-align: center;
    padding-bottom: 1rem;
    padding-left: 1rem;
    padding-right: 1rem;
}

.art-container .art .image-container {
    padding: 0;
    min-height: 100%;
    max-width: 100%;
}

.art-container .art2 {
    flex: 0 3 180px;
    text-align: center;
    padding-bottom: 1rem;
    padding-left: 1rem;
    padding-right: 1rem;
}

.art-container .art2 .image-container {
    padding: 0;
    min-height: 100%;
    max-width: 100%;
}
[[/module]]

[[>]]
[[module Rate]]
[[/>]]

This is a collaborative page for GOC logos, representing various Divisions and Members of the Council of 108.

All designs on this page are derivative of work by [[*user Navla]], which are [https://scpko.wdfiles.com/local--files/navla-artwork/GOC.svg available here]. This work has been uploaded to this page by [[*user Jerden]] for ease of use in GOC Formats and other tales about the Coalition, alongside additional designs. 

People are welcome to contribute new icons to this page, just make sure to include the creator and image source in the License Box.
